  "story": "A powerful invocation bhajan sung across Pentecostal and charismatic churches in North India. This traditional hymn is a staple at revival meetings and prayer gatherings, calling upon the Holy Spirit to descend with power and fire. Its passionate melody has accompanied countless moments of spiritual awakening.",
